          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺、悟空。保护师父，去往西天取经。前者多蒙灵吉菩萨，降了黄风怪，过了\n黄风岭。一路行来，师父命我探路，前面已是流沙河，只怕有些难过，不免请\n出师父趱路。\n有请师父！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猪八戒、唐僧同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果生枝上终须熟，子在胞中岂有珠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见师父！"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了！啊悟空，命你前面探路，可曾探明？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀师父：弟子探得前面，乃是流沙河地界，只怕有些难过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "悟空，想你我出家之人，既已皈依三宝，讲什么道路难过？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猴儿哥，你只管放心，此番到了流沙河，我老猪会水，就是拖，也把你们爷儿\n俩拖过河去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不必多言，前面带路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉旨西来道路赊，\n秋风淅淅落霜花。\n意马初发鞭漫加。"
        },
        {
          "character": "心猿牢锁绳休解、孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀师父：此来已是河岸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！只见：一片流沙远，何处是渡头？果然一道大河横路，恁般波浪掀天，水\n势宽阔，又无船只来往，悟空，我们怎样过去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父不必着急，待弟子纵起空中，观看水势，再作道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空翻下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八戒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父！"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待等悟空回来，再作道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。孙悟空上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀师父：适才弟子起在空中，只见这河，有八百里宽阔，十分难渡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！这便怎么处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊师父，那旁有一碑碣，上面有字，你我向前看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧、孙悟空、猪八戒同趋前看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“流沙河”。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有四行小字呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宽阔八百流沙境，\n广远三千弱水深；\n点点芦花定底沉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急急风〗。八水卒、沙僧同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沙僧 （三笑） 哈哈，哈哈，啊哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（八水卒、沙僧同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猴儿哥，你看从水里冒出一个妖精来。你好生看守师父，我去会他一会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "须要小心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！妖怪休走！你猪八老爷擒你来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猪八戒下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，看八戒追赶妖魔去了，你我师徒登高眺望。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前面带路！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、唐僧同走圆场，同上高台。八水卒、沙僧同上。猪八戒上。八水卒、沙僧、猪八戒同会阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，妖精啊妖精！快快将我们渡过江去便罢，如若不然，呸，着耙！"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，大胆的丑鬼，胆敢追赶前来，休走，看杖！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（沙僧、猪八戒同起打，同拉下。八水卒同拥下。唐僧、孙悟空同下高台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，看八戒不是那妖怪的对手，师父且在那旁高坡稍息，待俺赶上前去，帮\n助于他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快去快回。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！\n妖怪休得猖狂，孙爷爷来也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空耍棍，下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "孙悟空→唐僧",
