    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "孙悟空",
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（八水卒、沙僧同上。猪八戒追上。沙僧、猪八戒同起打。八水卒同下。孙悟空上，起打。沙僧败下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿！我说猴儿哥，谁叫你来的？等我把他诓到高阜之处，你再来帮忙也不晚哪，\n如今他跳下水去啦，他还出来吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八戒，休要乱嚷。你再将他引出水来，俺在岸上接应于你就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可是这么着，我再把他诱出来，叫你动手，你再动手，可别忙喽！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺晓得。你快快前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺去也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猪八戒下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待俺去到高坡，禀告师父知道便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "猪八戒→孙悟空",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "孙悟空→猪八戒",
          "turns": 2
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 3,
