    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "他的膂利千斤大",
        "八水卒",
        "只因吴刚来伐下",
        "小妖",
        "此番定将他拿下",
        "沙僧",
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖乱锤〗。八水卒同上，同挖门。沙僧上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "适才山坡去玩耍，\n来了腌脏一僧家。\n未能取胜将他拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "他的膂利千斤大、小妖",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小妖上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "小妖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岸上有个僧人讨战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": "小妖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小妖下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻言不由烈火发，\n野僧擅敢叫骂咱！\n擒进水府将他杀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "此番定将他拿下、沙僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众水卒，迎敌者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "八水卒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（八水卒、沙僧同走圆场。猪八戒上。八水卒、沙僧、猪八戒同会阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！妖怪呀妖怪！你战我弟兄不过，就该将我师徒渡过河去，饶你性命。如若\n不然，你猪八老爷钯齿厉害，这一钯就是九个窟窿，你是怕也不怕？"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！不怕死的秃驴，可知俺宝杖的厉害！"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！你别不害臊啦，凭你那根棍，有什么来头？"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我这宝杖来头大，\n月中棱罗树枝杈！\n鲁班制造赠某家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "只因吴刚来伐下、猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "只因吴刚来伐下、猪八戒",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孽畜休要夸大话，\n竟敢混充是仙家。\n一钯叫你回老家。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猪八戒、沙僧同起打。猪八戒败下。沙僧、八水卒同追下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
