    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "八水卒",
        "孙悟空",
        "沙僧"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。孙悟空上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！看八戒与那妖怪争斗，虽然不分胜负，终是不能成功。待俺纵起云头，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空上桌。猪八戒上。八水卒、沙僧同追上。猪八戒、沙僧同起打。孙悟空下高桌，起打。沙僧、八水"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众水卒，急回水府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "八水卒",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（八水卒、沙僧同入水，同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
