    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "孙悟空",
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪八戒同上，望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哟！得！猴儿哥，你看见了没有，他又跳下水去啦！这可怎么好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八戒，你看这妖怪被你我战怕，他不敢出来，你我师徒怎生过去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猴儿哥，这我可一点儿法子没有啦！你我见过师父，商量个主意再说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言之有理。走！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪八戒同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "猪八戒→孙悟空",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "孙悟空→猪八戒",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 2,
          "白": 4
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "唐僧",
        "孙悟空",
        "猪八戒"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人生颠沛终难免，\n总要心如铁石坚。\n一心拜佛去西天。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪八戒同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "适才与妖来交战，\n果然武艺非等闲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猴儿哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我见了师父面，\n交战之事说一番。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空、猪八戒",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见师父！"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了！啊悟空，你等与那妖怪交战，胜负如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊师父，我和八戒与那妖怪交战，他不是对手，跳进水去，再不出来。为此前\n来，禀明师父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，流沙河这样难过，不知几时得到西天？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，我倒有个主意。你我师徒拨转马头，回朝复命。您哪就说：咱们到了西\n天，见了活佛，磕完了头，佛爷让咱们爷儿们吃斋，只顾一欢喜，把取经的事，\n就给忘啦。倘若那唐王再叫您去取经，变着法儿撒谎不去，什么脑袋疼啦，\n肚子疼啦，给他个胡说。这差事不就搪过去了吗？我还是回我的高老庄，猴儿\n哥回他的花果山，岂不三全其美吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蠢材，休得胡说！我若不到西天，岂不辜负唐王圣意，枉称了御弟之名，真真\n岂有此理！"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪八戒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，您别生我的气，我这是胡说八道，还是听我猴儿哥的吧。我说猴儿哥有\n什么主意没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父不必烦恼，待弟子去往普陀山，求菩萨指引指引，倘能过去，也未可知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若前去，须要早去早回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！八戒，你好生在此看守师父，俺就此去也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辞别师父把路趱，\n求菩萨指引好到西天。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见悟空云程远，\n待他回来上西天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八戒随我来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧、猪八戒同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "唐僧→孙悟空",
          "turns": 3
