          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猪八戒、孙悟空、八水卒、沙僧自两边分上，同起打。四神兵、青龙、白虎、玄坛、灵官、伽蓝、哪吒、"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金吒、木吒同上，同摆阵，同开打，擒沙僧。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "木吒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "悟净，你今被擒，还不皈依唐僧么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，原来是菩萨派遣来的天兵天将！\n啊众位法官，俺也曾受过菩萨慈训，言道唐三藏乃是我的师父，他若到来，我\n便皈依。"
        },
        {
          "character": "木吒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "悟空，快请你师父前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n有请师父！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉命取经文，魔难不离身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "悟空，何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "菩萨遣动天兵天将，前来收伏妖怪，如今皈依佛门，师父向前见过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。待为师向前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青龙、白虎、玄坛、灵官、伽蓝、哪吒、金吒、木吒",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "法师！"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳众位天神，擒伏妖孽，愿圣寿无疆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "木吒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "悟净，你师父到了，还不向前礼拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n弟子愚昧无知，不知师父到此，多有冒犯。情愿皈依佛门，侍奉师父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，待我与你起个法名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弟子也曾受过菩萨戒行。以沙为姓，取名悟净，愿保师父西行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "木吒",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "菩萨法谕，这有葫芦一个。将你项上骷髅骨摘下，化做法船，你师徒四人渡过\n流沙河便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "菩萨慈悲，待我望空一拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "青龙、白虎、玄坛、灵官、伽蓝、哪吒、金吒、木吒",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等护送法师一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就不敢！有日取经回来，焚香叩谢，告辞了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧、孙悟空、猪八戒、沙僧同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "青龙、白虎、玄坛、灵官、伽蓝、哪吒、金吒、木吒",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等复命去者！\n（四神兵、青龙、白虎、玄坛、灵官、伽蓝、哪吒、金吒、木吒同下。〖牌子〗。挡围幕，摆船，船作葫芦\n式，船头安九个骷髅骨。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沙僧 （内同白） 开船那！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
